    "Model diagnostics confirmed no major assumption violations; see Appendix C [17].",
    "Statistical Tests for Scale IndependenceTo test whether model identity or parameter count better characterizes identity disclosure patterns, we adopted a three-part statistical approach.",
    "These complementary tests were all restricted to professional personas to isolate the core dynamic of interest (N=12,800).",
